message: /* vpnoverview on spam blacklist */ new section
I removed José Manuel Barroso as President of the European Commission and replaced him with Jean-Claud Juncker.
/* VPN blocking by online services */ I added another streaming service that blocks VPN users, Disney Plus.
/* Terminology */ I added some more info on the Dark Web and the differences between it and the Deep Web (by including information on the differences in accessibility).
/* Features */ I added more information about the NordLynx protocol and its advantages and included a citation for this info (since there was a "citation missing" label).
/* Definition */ Added another often used classification system of big data, based on its source.

page: List of websites blocked in mainland China
message: /* Table of high-ranking websites blocked in mainland China */ Added a site (Tinder) and a source for this.
I added a sentence under the header "description" to discuss another technique that some VPN providers use to combat VPN blocks. I also added a reference for this information.
I added a reference.
I added a citation after the very first sentence.
/* SMS phishing */ I added a more modern form of Smishing, called WhatsApp fraud and included a reference.
I added a citation after the definition of big data.
